tool_description:
HealthCare.gov for Developers
We’re making our source code freely available on GitHub. All of our educational content about the Health Insurance Marketplace is available in machine-readable formats so that innovators, entrepreneurs, and partners can turn it into new products and services.
name: Healthcare.gov
title: Healthcare.gov

api_list.name: Content objects
api_list.description: Content objects: the body content and metadata for each post on this website
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://community-healthcaregov.p.rapidapi.com/what-is-the-health-insurance-marketplace.json"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "community-healthcaregov.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
